# Maximum File Length: 200 Lines

Every source file MUST be 200 lines or fewer. No exceptions.

## When a file approaches or exceeds 200 lines

1. Extract sub-components into separate files
2. Move helper functions to a `utils` or `lib` file
3. Move types/interfaces to a dedicated `.types.ts` file
4. Move constants to a dedicated `constants.ts` file
5. Split large components into smaller, composed pieces

## Example — splitting a large component

```
// ❌ BAD: one 350-line file
src/components/TransactionDetail.tsx (350 lines)

// ✅ GOOD: split into focused files
src/components/transaction-detail/TransactionInfo.tsx (60 lines)
src/components/transaction-detail/SettlementForm.tsx (80 lines)
src/components/transaction-detail/StatusTimeline.tsx (50 lines)
src/components/transaction-detail/index.tsx (40 lines)
```
